reviews.comment: I'm very impressed by this creator. We described the logo needs and let them have free reign. They sent over 4 different logos within 24 hours, all of which were pretty good and totally usable as it. We selected one of them and tweaked a bit but that was to make it to our taste, not to correct for any artistic issues. I really like that the 4 options were TOTALLY different from each other, so many creators here will say they'll give you 3 or 4 different logos and they're all basically the same with slightly different fonts of whatever. These looked like 4 different artists took a shot at it so it legit gave us artistic directions. Top notch work and highly recommended.

the designs they provided were not really what I was looking for, I was expecting something better, so I created my own design and asked them to create it as well. I will not give 1 or 2 stars anyway as they have been at all time proactive and open to anything I asked to them

Moon is the greatest. Professional, prompt, patient and dedicated. 

Moon really took our project up. 
I highly and happily recommend Moon to anyone who needs a great design.

Next, we will keep miving witg this seller. Nothing else to say.

Everything was great and I feel like it was better than some AI site could do at this point. Communication was clear and arrived promptly without delays. I liked the several different options presented to choose from or mix and match. She was able to customize an icon to my specific need.

To be completely honest, I had no real visualization of the logo I wanted, so I simply described to Moon what I generally wanted. Just like last time, her creativity is really impressive, and she not only delivered hours before our agreed deadline, but she also added several complimentary social media mockups. I can tell that Moon is very hard-working and I appreciate her prompt replies--I'll definitely be back for more orders and I can confidently say that she is a great logo designer.
